data.description:
This charming 1879 sq ft, four-bedroom/One bath home is
nestled in the heart of Anaconda, Montana. Start planning and put
down roots in this affordable home in the Rocky Mountains. Great
proximity to downtown, schools and parks. The home features
three levels, a private back yard which is a blank slate to be
transformed into a small garden or entertaining area and is ready
for your creative touch.
Do you need extra storage space? This home offers a detached
garage divided into two spaces. Convert to a shop or something
more specific.
Anaconda is home to stunning natural scenery, with hiking trails,
fishing, and camping close by. Only a short drive to Georgetown
Lake or Discovery Ski Area. Other community attractions include
a Jack Nicklaus signature design golf Course and Fairmont Hot
springs Resort. During the summer months, go to the weekly
farmers market and enjoy the many vendors and entertainment.
Regardless, live, play and enjoy what Anaconda has to offer.
